title: Kirill Kochubei
text:
Kirill Aleksandrovich Kochubei (; born 6 October 1986) is a Russian former <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>.
Club career.
He made two appearances (67 mins.) for <a href="PFC%20CSKA%20Moscow">CSKA Moscow</a> in <a href="UEFA%20Champions%20League%202006-07">UEFA Champions League 2006-07</a>.
